==Bundles==
The peach is an option for the {{Bundle|Artisan||y}}.

==Recipes==
The peach is not used in any recipes.

==Tailoring==
The peach can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring#Pants|Relaxed Fit Shorts]]. [[File:Relaxed Fit Shorts.png|36px]] It also can be used as a red dye color in the Dye Pots, found inside [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
The peach is not used in any [[quests]].

==History==
{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].}}

